content: Based on the information provided, Prince Oreoluwa Abidakun has a Master's degree in Clinical Social Work (MSSW) from the University of Tennessee-Knoxville and has been a Licensed Master Social Worker (LMSW). He has experience as a therapist and a psychiatric social worker, which would qualify him for an LCSW (Licensed Clinical Social Worker) position in Texas, provided he has met the required supervised experience and passed the necessary licensing exams. However, he does not have the qualifications to be a psychiatrist, as that requires a medical degree and specialized training in psychiatry.
